. I think the broader worry is that if the SEC approves an easy attractive =
crypto-investing product, there will be more retail crypto investing, and t=
he SEC kind of doesn=E2=80=99t want that. =E2=80=9CGrayscale-SEC Fight Coul=
d Clear the Way for Anybody to Speculate on Bitcoin=E2=80=9D is <a href=3D"=
