tom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; b=
ackground-color: #ccc;"> Regulation M</a> under the US securities laws <a h=
ref=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/30759013.257411/aHR0cH=
M6Ly93d3cubGF3LmNvcm5lbGwuZWR1L2Nmci90ZXh0LzE3LzI0Mi4xMDE/607f07ceef4b8524a=
